roadway production to be performed in India, currently playing at the recently inaugurated <a href="https://nmacc.com/performing-arts/the-sound-of-music?gclid=CjwKCAjwjYKjBhB5EiwAiFdSfinG8yqncrmx3K2-nqjGfNBw93g4r0XSYfAH6XMivjuqC8zykW_WMxoCKicQAvD_BwE">NMACC</a> in Mumbai.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7ef595e-04e0-4059-aef1-b142c9ae0f06_592x702.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7ef595e-04e0-4059-aef1-b142c9ae0f06_592x702.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7ef595e-04e0-4059-aef1-b142c9ae0f06_592x702.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7ef595e-04e0-4059-aef1-b142c9ae0f06_592x702.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7ef595e-04e0-4059-aef1-b142c9ae0f06_592x702.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7ef595e-04e0-4059-aef1-b142c9ae0f06_592x702.png" width="440" height="521.7567567567568" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a7ef595e-04e0-4059-aef1-b142c9ae0f06_592x702.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWaterma