ahul/Downloads/Economic%20Survey%20Complete%20PDF%20(1).pdf">Economic Survey of India (2023)</a> depicting the exponential growth of India&#8217;s groundbreaking real-time mobile payments platform - <a href="https://tigerfeathers.substack.com/p/the-internet-country">UPI (Unified Payments Interface)</a>. UPI payments accounted for 52% of all digital transactions in India in 2022.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F03c8a790-96a5-4123-aa70-d9b6c4838890_744x391.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F03c8a790-96a5-4123-aa70-d9b6c4838890_744x391.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F03c8a790-96a5-4123-aa70-d9b6c4838890_744x391.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F03c8a790-96a5-4123-aa70-d9b6c4838890_744x391.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F03c8a790-96a5-4123-aa70-d9b6c4838890_744x391.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F03c8a790-96a5-4123-aa70-d9b6c4838890_744x391.jpeg" width="652" height="342.6505376344086" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-