-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg" width="578" height="537.2" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:632,&quot;width&quot;:680,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:578,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Image" title="Image" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F46e928db-5318-48cc-a5dc-1f780501cd90_680x632.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>You get the idea.</p><p>Anyway, like I said up top, it would have been fun to present a vision of 21st century India through a montage of pretty diagrams. I still have several other serviceable charts on things like airports, exports, highways, bank deposits, tigers and <a href="https://twitter.com/TanaySukumar/status/1635205727441809409?s=20">Oscar-winning songs</a> that would make for great additions to this piece. </p><p>But halfway through my research process, I realised that many of the themes I wanted to explore were best illustrated not via charts but rather by the stories of entrepreneurs and startups that were building companies in those same areas. </p><p>For instance, I was looking for data on the <a href="https://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/the-meat-category-suffers-due-to-indias-cultural-hypocrisy-licious-co-founder-9229111.html">$65 bn meat consumption market in India</a>, but I figured I could make my point better by highlighting the story of <strong><a href="https://www.licious.in/">Licious</a></strong>, an 8-year old company which has built the <a href="https://techcrunch.com/2022/03/14/indias-licious-raises-150-million-for-its-fresh-animal-protein-e-commerce-platform/">&#8220;highest valued D2C start-up in India</a>&#8221; by selling fresh meat and seafood products online. Licious is a perfect example of the kind of narrative violation I was hoping to ensnare for this piece, having built a billion dollar company selling animal protein in a country that people would typically (<a href="https://twitter.com/Stats_of_India/status/1529687856243175425">and wrongly</a>) assume skews overwhelmingly vegetarian. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png" width="991" height="506" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:506,&quot;width&quot;:991,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;How To Create a Meat Delivery App Like Licious - Complete Guide&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;How To Create a Meat Delivery App Like Licious - Complete Guide&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="How To Create a Meat Delivery App Like Licious - Complete Guide" title="How To Create a Meat Delivery App Like Licious - Complete Guide" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe492a9f4-f85e-4a47-b600-fa56d4aefda5_991x506.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: RedBytes</figcaption></figure></div><p>Or take the example of religion in India. You could perhaps argue that religiosity is an unavoidable casualty of a &#8216;smartening&#8217; populace, incompatible with the bells and whistles of the modern world. I could probably show you data that argues both ways. But in reality, tradition and technology are proving to be strangely congenial bedfellows. This is illustrated perfectly by the story of <a href="https://www.srimandir.com/">SriMandir</a> (<a href="https://tigerfeathers.substack.com/p/10-million-users-and-rising-fast">which we covered in March</a>), a uniquely Indian application that aims to &#8216;put a temple in every phone&#8217;. SriMandir&#8217;s 10 million+ users invalidate the claim that devotion and digitisation can&#8217;t peacefully co-exist.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png" width="1456" height="561" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:561,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3ae63e7-ad6c-4e7b-8885-2e1645db5894_2512x968.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: SriMandir/AppsForBharat</figcaption></figure></div><p>Similarly, you&#8217;d struggle to find an area of Indian society that hasn&#8217;t been touched by technology. We probably still take for granted how different our routines were just 10 years ago when UPI didn&#8217;t exist, Jio hadn&#8217;t yet launched, and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016_Indian_banknote_demonetisation">1000 rupee notes</a> were still a thing. So, given that our newsletter typically covers stories from the Indian startup ecosystem, I thought I could make my case better by focusing on the <em><strong>products</strong></em> that capture how India is changing.</p><blockquote><p><em>&#8220;We shape our tools and thereafter our tools shape us&#8221; <br>- </em><strong>John Culkin (A Schoolman&#8217;s Guide to Marshall McLuhan)</strong></p></blockquote><p>Before we begin, first, a few disclaimers:</p><ol><li><p>This is a &#8216;shallower&#8217; piece than our usual fare. It&#8217;s more of a mood board than a manuscript. Closer to Buzzfeed than <a href="https://stratechery.com/">Ben Thompson</a>. You can think of it as a tasting menu of India in 2023. </p></li><li><p>This isn&#8217;t <em>just</em> a list of products. It&#8217;s really a mish-mash of products, themes, sectors and innovations that deserve their own chapter in modern Indian folklore. Our only qualifying criteria was that each of these topics should be interesting enough to warrant a future deep dive.</p></li><li><p>You don&#8217;t have to read it in one sitting. Treat it as a 10-part anthology as opposed to a 10-act Shakespearean play.</p></li></ol><p>Mostly, I wanted this piece to serve as an answer to the question &#8220;what can I read to get a flavour for what&#8217;s happening in India?&#8221; If you like this format, let us know and we&#8217;ll do it more often.</p><p>Anyway, let&#8217;s get going. Here are the <strong>&#8216;10(ish) Products That Capture How India Is Changing&#8217;</strong>&#127470;&#127475;</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://tigerfeathers.substack.com/p/10ish-products-that-capture-how-india?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://tigerfeathers.substack.com/p/10ish-products-that-capture-how-india?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>Share</span></a></p><div><hr></div><h1>1&#65039;&#8419;<strong> Tea&#9749;</strong></h1><p>Are you familiar with the "<a href="https://www.npr.org/2010/03/28/125237353/the-tea-thieves-how-a-drink-shaped-an-empire">greatest single act of corporate espionage in history</a>"?</p><p>It has nothing to do with Apple or Samsung or HP or Volkswagen, or any other modern corporations you read about in the news these days. No, this act took place in the 1800s. It involved a British horticulturalist named Robert Fortune. The theft in question targeted the secrets of tea cultivation in China. </p><p>The British were looking to reduce their dependence on Chinese tea in the wake of the <em><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opium_Wars">Opium Wars</a></em>. They had fallen in love with &#8216;the beverage&#8217;, and couldn&#8217;t rely on a hostile Qing dynasty anymore to fill their cups. They realised they could puncture the Chinese monopoly on tea by initiating the cultivation of tea in their territories in India (parts of which shared a similar climate profile to China). So in the mid-19th century, the East India Company recruited the services of Robert Fortune (AKA &#8216;The Tea Thief&#8217;). He spent years on a covert mission across the border, using a variety of tricks and disguises to smuggle plants and farming techniques out of China to seed the growth of tea in India. That&#8217;s how the story of tea in India began, as a consequence of colonial conflict. </p><p>Before the East India Company realised the commercial potential of tea as a commodity, tea was mainly consumed in India as a form of medicine, to help with mild ailments like headaches and indigestion.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png" width="960" height="320" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:320,&quot;width&quot;:960,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:775990,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7170421c-1921-4867-8c2c-92743254b25a_960x320.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: iStock/Dreamstime</figcaption></figure></div><p>It was only in the early 1900s, with the mushrooming of roadside stalls and Irani Cafes in every corner of the country (coupled with savvy advertising that bordered on propaganda) that tea became &#8216;India&#8217;s drink&#8217;. The culture of tea drinking was intertwined with the nationalism and enlightenment that characterised India&#8217;s freedom movement in the lead up to Independence.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png" width="933" height="447" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:447,&quot;width&quot;:933,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:932145,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc36ebacd-2c83-479f-a11c-d08b4844f638_933x447.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Image Sources: SeriesEats / Scroll / Priya Paul collection</figcaption></figure></div><p>These days the culture of tea drinking has been given a facelift, appropriately reflecting the heightening aspirations of India&#8217;s modern working class. Tea isn&#8217;t just a way to start the day in 2023 India, but a <em>place</em> to to continue the conversation. Startups like <a href="https://shop.chaipoint.com/">Chai Point</a> and <a href="https://cafes.chaayos.com/">Chaayos</a> (started in 2010 and 2012 respectively) have enrobed the humble cup of chai in a slick modern avatar, replicating the same formula that Starbucks employed to ignite the culture of coffee drinking in the West. </p><p>As the two leading chains in India&#8217;s <a href="https://retail.economictimes.indiatimes.com/blog/outlook-of-the-luxury-tea-market-in-2022/95210350">tea cafe scene</a>, they&#8217;ve become mainstays in retail hubs all over the country, gobbling up considerable <a href="https://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/companies/chai-points-growth-ambition-rides-on-vending-machines-8690451.html">venture capital</a> along the way to aid their rapid expansion. Their outlets provide a &#8216;premium&#8217; alternative to tea brewed at home or at traditional roadside stalls. Their menus feature unconventional (sacrilegious?) flavours like &#8216;aam papad chai&#8217; and &#8216;rose cardamom&#8217; chai; they&#8217;ve even built <a href="https://entrackr.com/2018/01/chaayos-launches-chai-monk/">IoT-enabled robots</a> to standardise production. Following the contemporary <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fast-food_restaurant">QSR</a> playbook, these companies are experimenting with deliveries, B2B sales, franchises, and vending machines, using creativity and technology to build commercial empires around &#8216;India&#8217;s drink&#8217;.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png" width="877" height="564" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:564,&quot;width&quot;:877,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1116258,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2f1e10cd-7f3a-4c95-9301-63153f90b25c_877x564.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source (clockwise from top right): Chaayos, Roastea, Chai Sutta Bar, Chai Point</figcaption></figure></div><p>Along the way they&#8217;ve been joined by plucky competitors like <a href="https://yourstory.com/smbstory/ahmedabad-chai-tea-coffee-business-roastea-lawyer-entrepreneurs">Roastea</a>, <a href="https://www.timesnownews.com/business-economy/anubhav-dubey-chai-sutta-bar-co-founder-man-who-made-chai-his-business-model-now-sells-tea-worth-rs-150-crore-per-year-net-worth-article-100291429">Chai Sutta Bar</a>, Chai Break, <a href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/too-many-tea-breaks-turned-them-into-chai-kings/articleshow/92796150.cms">Chai Kings</a>, <a href="https://lifestyle.livemint.com/news/big-story/how-kausshal-dugarr-of-teabox-made-tea-sexy-111620318825852.html">Teabox</a>, <a href="https://yourstory.com/smbstory/mba-chaiwala-entrepreneur-prafull-billore-tea-business-success-story">MBA Chaiwalla</a> and others, each of whom is adding their own twist to the <a href="https://www.financialexpress.com/business/brandwagon-reading-the-tea-leaves-from-chai-to-high-tea-2652582/">tea cafe experience</a>. Many of India&#8217;s major tea producers have also expanded <a href="https://www.financialexpress.com/business/brandwagon-why-are-homegrown-tea-companies-foraying-into-quick-service-restaurants-1728338/">downstream</a>, opening boutique cafes and bars to offer the perfect sanctuary for tea connoisseurs.</p><p>Not to be left behind, even the original roadside chai stall has been fitted for an upgrade. One of the major success stories from the last season of Shark Tank India was a company named <a href="https://mahantam.co.in/">Mahantam</a>. Started by two brothers in their early 20s, Mahantam makes an automatic tea glass-washing machine for roadside tea stalls that can wash 15 tea glasses in 30 seconds. Their pitch was only the second time in the season where <a href="https://in.mashable.com/entertainment/46973/pitcher-impresses-shark-tank-india-judges-with-his-tea-glass-washing-machine-innovation-bags-all-5-s">every shark on the panel</a> joined forces to invest.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png" width="1456" height="819" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Mahantam Shark Tank India Season 2 Episode 29 | Chai Glass Washer Machine - Shark  Tank India&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Mahantam Shark Tank India Season 2 Episode 29 | Chai Glass Washer Machine - Shark  Tank India&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Mahantam Shark Tank India Season 2 Episode 29 | Chai Glass Washer Machine - Shark  Tank India" title="Mahantam Shark Tank India Season 2 Episode 29 | Chai Glass Washer Machine - Shark  Tank India" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c96ed70-f5ce-461e-9337-88764a8701fd_1536x864.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Link to the full pitch <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hy8AdDppce4&amp;embeds_referring_euri=https%3A%2F%2Fsharktank.co.in%2F&amp;source_ve_path=MjM4NTE&amp;feature=emb_title&amp;ab_channel=BanterWithChetan">here</a> (via Shark Tank India)</figcaption></figure></div><p>Whatever your preference, there&#8217;s enough room in India&#8217;s tea industry for everyone to flourish. India consumed <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/870829/india-consumption-volume-of-tea/">1.2 billion kg</a> of tea in 2022. It is said that <a href="https://www.ibef.org/blogs/the-tea-industry-in-india#:~:text=Production%20%26%20Exports%20Scenario,of%20the%20country's%20tea%20production.">80% of all Indian families</a> drink tea. Despite the fact that we are the second largest producer of tea in the world (after China), it is telling that <a href="https://www.ibef.org/blogs/the-tea-industry-in-india#:~:text=Production%20%26%20Exports%20Scenario,of%20the%20country's%20tea%20production.">80-90%</a> of this tea is consumed domestically. It is as close to a narcotic as you&#8217;ll find in India without alerting the authorities, and the ritual of tea drinking is one that shows no signs of going away anytime soon.</p><p>One of the major themes of Indian enterprise in the 2010s was a shift from informal to formal, from unorganised to organised. You see it across different  industries and verticals - perhaps most notably in India&#8217;s cherished cup of chai.</p><div><hr></div><h1>2&#65039;&#8419;<strong> IPL&#127951;</strong></h1><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg" width="1200" height="675" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:675,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;IPL 2023 Opening Ceremony Live: Rashmika, Tamanna &amp; Arjit All Set To Dazzle  At The IPL Inaugural&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;IPL 2023 Opening Ceremony Live: Rashmika, Tamanna &amp; Arjit All Set To Dazzle  At The IPL Inaugural&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="IPL 2023 Opening Ceremony Live: Rashmika, Tamanna &amp; Arjit All Set To Dazzle  At The IPL Inaugural" title="IPL 2023 Opening Ceremony Live: Rashmika, Tamanna &amp; Arjit All Set To Dazzle  At The IPL Inaugural" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa516a830-3a1f-4022-87f7-c73345710c31_1200x675.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: BQ Prime</figcaption></figure></div><p>The Indian Premier League is the closest thing that India has to a contemporary religious festival. The deities may take a different form, but the intensity of devotion is undeniable. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg" width="634" height="356.625" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/bfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1280,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:634,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;IPL 2019 SRH vs CSK: Twitter outrage as Chennai fans asked to leave CSK  flags, Dhoni posters outside Hyderabad stadium&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;IPL 2019 SRH vs CSK: Twitter outrage as Chennai fans asked to leave CSK  flags, Dhoni posters outside Hyderabad stadium&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="IPL 2019 SRH vs CSK: Twitter outrage as Chennai fans asked to leave CSK  flags, Dhoni posters outside Hyderabad stadium" title="IPL 2019 SRH vs CSK: Twitter outrage as Chennai fans asked to leave CSK  flags, Dhoni posters outside Hyderabad stadium" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbfd521cd-d0d3-486a-b7a3-837f4a785969_1280x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: DNA India</figcaption></figure></div><p>For two months between March and May every year, <s>no one gets anything done</s> India tunes into the IPL. You&#8217;d struggle to find a television set (or smartphone) that isn&#8217;t adorned with colourful broadcasts from the biggest club cricket tournament on the planet. Still only in its 16th season, the IPL is speed-running the process of building an iconic sports league that already stands shoulder-to-shoulder with globally renowned (and historic) entertainment franchises like the English Premier League, UFC, F1, the NFL, NBA etc. </p><p>It is already the <a href="https://www.joincolossus.com/episodes/5270704/cowan-ipl-reinventing-cricket?tab=transcript">second-most valuable sports property</a> in the world when measured by the price of media rights. The price of broadcasting an IPL game comes in at $15 million per game compared to the $36 million per game for the NFL. Over <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/sports/high-octane-ipl-matches-take-tv-digital-viewership-to-new-highs/articleshow/100168937.cms?from=mdr">450 million unique viewers</a> in India tuned in to the IPL last year, reaching roughly half of the total television sets in the country. Given that 93% of all sports hours watched in India are cricket, the IPL is the closest thing we have to a unifying cultural force. However, contrary to the Superbowl, which serves a similar function in the US, the IPL isn&#8217;t just one game. It&#8217;s an entire two-month span where the attention of India (and the global cricketing audience) is affixed on the same stage.</p><p>The IPL&#8217;s inclusion on this list isn&#8217;t because of its ascendance as a globally significant sports property. It&#8217;s because the IPL itself has become a reflection of India&#8217;s evolution since 2008 (when the league was inaugurated).</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png" width="1029" height="470" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:470,&quot;width&quot;:1029,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:166755,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9c25213e-7cd7-4d42-9793-fedd2c9ea55f_1029x470.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Chinese smartphone maker Vivo was contracted to hold the title sponsorship from 2016-2022 but had to suspend their status in 2020 owing to public pressure as a result of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020%E2%80%932021_China%E2%80%93India_skirmishes">border stand-off</a> between India and China. They were back in 2021 but had to forego their final year of sponsorship owing to the same geopolitical tensions. In 2022 and 2023, as startups began to watch their wallets more closely, the IPL title sponsorship passed into the safe hands of the Tata Group, probably India&#8217;s most esteemed legacy business institution [Original image source: <a href="https://startuptalky.com/how-indian-startups-sponsored-ipl/">StartupTalky</a>]</figcaption></figure></div><p>You see it in the rotating cast of corporations that have scrambled to place themselves in front of the IPL audience. These companies - paying <a href="https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/news/how-start-ups-are-upping-their-ipl-sponsorship-game/article65308828.ece">sky high ad rates</a> - are those at a stage in their trajectories where it makes sense to swap money for eyeballs. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg" width="668" height="434.2" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:520,&quot;width&quot;:800,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:668,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Revisiting brand-team partnerships from IPL 2008&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Revisiting brand-team partnerships from IPL 2008&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Revisiting brand-team partnerships from IPL 2008" title="Revisiting brand-team partnerships from IPL 2008" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb1a40b42-4792-4fcf-a582-0be0f6849dae_800x520.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">In the inaugural year of the IPL (2008), with India only 17 years removed from its landmark <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economic_liberalisation_in_India#:~:text=Indian%20economic%20liberalisation%20was%20part,liberalisation%20was%20initiated%20in%201991.">economic liberalisation</a> of 1991, sponsorships were dominated by traditional enterprise giants from industries like telecom, construction, financial services and consumer goods.  (Image source: <a href="https://www.campaignindia.in/article/revisiting-brand-team-partnerships-from-ipl-2008/482629">Campaign India</a>)</figcaption></figure></div><p>Last year, with India coming off a <a href="https://entrackr.com/2022/01/indian-startups-raised-38-billion-in-2021-entrackr-report/">record year of venture capital funding in 2021</a>, IPL screens and jerseys and stadiums were peppered with logos from startups that were flush with cash and eager to force their way into public consciousness.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg" width="440" height="615.4301572617946" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1512,&quot;width&quot;:1081,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:440,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Startups Catch The Cricket Fever! 29 Indian Startups At Tata IPL 2022&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Startups Catch The Cricket Fever! 29 Indian Startups At Tata IPL 2022&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Startups Catch The Cricket Fever! 29 Indian Startups At Tata IPL 2022" title="Startups Catch The Cricket Fever! 29 Indian Startups At Tata IPL 2022" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F72aef4f8-c7b2-4bec-91d1-37fd9e44c234_1081x1512.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: <a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Finc42.com%2Ffeatures%2Fstartups-catch-the-cricket-fever-29-indian-startups-take-to-the-pitch-at-tata-ipl-2022%2F&amp;psig=AOvVaw0pECAYtDjRoC-Lvuh4sYcp&amp;ust=1684841601218000&amp;source=images&amp;cd=vfe&amp;ved=0CBMQjhxqFwoTCKDF6qPqiP8CFQAAAAAdAAAAABAY">Inc42</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>The year before, in the midst of a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Everything_bubble">historic bubble</a> for high-risk assets, the IPL saw crypto startups dominate Indian airwaves for the first time. Practically mirroring the Indian government&#8217;s capricious position towards the <a href="https://tigerfeathers.substack.com/p/crypto-in-india">regulation of crypto</a>, these startups were <a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/tech/technology/top-cryptocurrency-exchanges-not-to-advertise-during-ipl/articleshow/90402672.cms?from=mdr">nowhere to be seen in 2022</a>, electing to play nice with the regulators&#8217; request for more responsible marketing of their products.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png" width="1044" height="278" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:278,&quot;width&quot;:1044,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:392104,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4826942b-e39f-48be-85c8-9e5482920b13_1044x278.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">India&#8217;s top crypto exchanges (Coinswitch Kuber and WazirX) made their presence felt in IPL 2021</figcaption></figure></div><p>As the global funding winter blew towards the subcontinent, Indian venture capital funding dropped by a third to $23.9 billion in 2022. The modus operandi for young companies flipped from offence to defence, with startups prioritising survival and profitability instead of pageantry and promotion. This was evident in this season&#8217;s IPL, when Indian startup participation <a href="https://www.livemint.com/news/india/ipl-2023-loses-sponsors-as-startups-unicorns-rationalise-costs-11679720892782.html">retreated proportionally</a> with the decrease in overall funding.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png" width="1456" height="728" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/dfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:728,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1086981,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdfbd4195-3d1c-460d-ab60-7bd960ac0c97_2232x1116.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/business-ipl-2023-exploring-latest-sponsorship-trends-the-media-ant/">The Media Ant</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>Marshall McLuhan once said that &#8220;Ads are the cave art of the twentieth century.&#8221; As far as India goes, if you want to know where the attention of our country is shifting, the writing is usually on the walls (of the IPL).</p><div><hr></div><h1>3&#65039;&#8419;<strong> Sex&#127820;</strong></h1><p>Despite India being the land of the Kama Sutra, it wouldn&#8217;t be unfair to say that conventional attitudes around marriage and sex can be conservative, at best, and repressed, at worst.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png" width="634" height="357.9032258064516" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:700,&quot;width&quot;:1240,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:634,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Indian Matchmaking' Season 3: Fans slam Sima Taparia as 'ignorant' for her  views on divorce | MEAWW&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Indian Matchmaking' Season 3: Fans slam Sima Taparia as 'ignorant' for her  views on divorce | MEAWW&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Indian Matchmaking' Season 3: Fans slam Sima Taparia as 'ignorant' for her  views on divorce | MEAWW" title="Indian Matchmaking' Season 3: Fans slam Sima Taparia as 'ignorant' for her  views on divorce | MEAWW" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6638acd9-930c-4696-a8f3-49574b9c6f84_1240x700.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">From the (somehow) international sensation &#8216;<em>Indian Matchmaking</em>&#8217; on Netflix</figcaption></figure></div><p>But they&#8217;re also changing. If you look past the <a href="https://homegrown.co.in/homegrown-voices/politics-sex-drugs-8-indian-films-that-were-banned-by-the-censor-board">censorship</a> and pearl-clutching that characterises much of our mainstream discourse, you can find tangible evidence of a thawing prudishness in Indian society, particularly amongst the younger generation. What&#8217;s more encouraging is that this changing tide has even spilled over to &#8216;Tier-2&#8217; and &#8216;Tier-3&#8217; India, outside the relatively liberal bubbles of India&#8217;s major cities.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg" width="351" height="535.3995943204868" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:752,&quot;width&quot;:493,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:351,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F58eaffd3-5777-4a31-8569-966763f284be_493x752.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Indian spent $9.9 million on dating and friendship apps in 2022, more than double what they spent the year before (Image Source: <a href="https://www.livemint.com/technology/tech-news/post-pandemic-dating-apps-see-surge-in-users-from-small-towns-and-cities-11664303006467.html">Livemint</a>)</figcaption></figure></div><p>It&#8217;s not just the process of <em>finding</em> romantic partners that&#8217;s changing, but the celebration of romance itself. A number of <a href="https://www.gqindia.com/relationships/content/6-best-sexual-pleasure-and-wellness-brands-to-shop-from-all-homegrown">startups</a> have broken ground in India&#8217;s nascent sexual wellness and sexual health space. These companies - like MyMuse, The Sassy Thing, Manzuri, Besharam and others - are crafting world class products for the Indian bedroom, using playful marketing and modern design to normalise the &#8216;right to pleasure&#8217; amongst Indian consumers.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png" width="886" height="555" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:555,&quot;width&quot;:886,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:938273,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F27d20939-151c-4cc6-9007-0ca8af2d19b8_886x555.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mymuse.in/?hl=en">@MyMuse.in</a> on Instagram</figcaption></figure></div><p><a href="https://mymuse.in/">MyMuse</a>, a venture-funded startup founded by husband-and-wife duo Anushka and Sahil Gupta, is building &#8216;India&#8217;s first luxury intimate wellness brand&#8217;. They say that 20% of the demand for their range of premium toys, massagers, oils, lubricants, candles and games comes from Tier-2 India.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26a52fb2-9060-45ca-9d02-8b2234d590c1_1230x684.png" data-component